282
00:18:38,339 --> 00:18:39,859
[SPEAKER_00] to je bila bitka kod jela Lameina.

283
00:18:39,859 --> 00:18:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

284
00:18:41,039 --> 00:18:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što svi mi vodimo bitku u sebi.

285
00:18:44,119 --> 00:18:46,759
[SPEAKER_00] Postoji bitka koju vodimo,

286
00:18:46,759 --> 00:18:49,599
[SPEAKER_00] koja se naziva i duhovni boj.

287
00:18:51,079 --> 00:18:51,720
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je to,

288
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] kao i kod Tomasa,

289
00:18:53,619 --> 00:18:55,019
[SPEAKER_00] tako i kod svih nas,

290
00:18:55,019 --> 00:18:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] bila bitka prekretnica za njega.

291
00:18:56,880 --> 00:18:59,220
[SPEAKER_00] Tu se je dvoumio

292
00:18:59,220 --> 00:19:00,980
[SPEAKER_00] da baci knjigu

293
00:19:00,980 --> 00:19:02,319
[SPEAKER_00] ili da je pročitao.

294
00:19:03,319 --> 00:19:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] Na njegovu radost,

295
00:19:04,539 --> 00:19:05,359
