298
00:19:10,460 --> 00:19:11,900
[SPEAKER_00] njegovih dijela.

299
00:19:11,900 --> 00:19:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] On je tu knjigu pročitao

300
00:19:15,039 --> 00:19:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] i ta knjiga ga je toliko dotakla

301
00:19:17,599 --> 00:19:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] da je izazvalo revoluciju

302
00:19:19,279 --> 00:19:20,079
