306
00:19:26,279 --> 00:19:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] bludničenja,

307
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:28,759
[SPEAKER_00] zabave,

308
00:19:28,759 --> 00:19:31,140
[SPEAKER_00] sve je ostavio po strani

309
00:19:31,140 --> 00:19:36,099
[SPEAKER_00] i krenuo potpuno drugačijim putem.

310
00:19:36,099 --> 00:19:39,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što ga duševelo

311
00:19:39,579 --> 00:19:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] u toj knjizi

312
00:19:40,380 --> 00:19:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] je to da je otkrio posebnu ideju

313
00:19:43,099 --> 00:19:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] Božje aseitas.

314
00:19:44,599 --> 00:19:47,599
[SPEAKER_00] To je Božju sposobnost

315
00:19:47,599 --> 00:19:50,579
[SPEAKER_00] da postigne,

316
00:19:50,579 --> 00:19:52,480
[SPEAKER_00] da postoji

317
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] po snazi svoje vlastite biti.

318
00:19:59,259 --> 00:20:01,359
[SPEAKER_00] Davam se da se sada možete

319
00:20:01,359 --> 00:20:02,480
[SPEAKER_00] svijetiti i vi vaših

320
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] bitka prekratnica,

321
00:20:04,460 --> 00:20:06,859
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno te knjige

322
00:20:06,859 --> 00:20:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] koja je kod njega izazvala revoluciju,

323
00:20:09,420 --> 00:20:12,200
[SPEAKER_00] da i sada vama napada na pamet

324
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:14,119
[SPEAKER_00] ili možda vama koji još niste

325
00:20:14,119 --> 00:20:15,339
[SPEAKER_00] obraćeni,

326
00:20:15,339 --> 00:20:16,859
[SPEAKER_00] da vam bar

327
00:20:16,859 --> 00:20:18,839
[SPEAKER_00] natuhnula nešto

328
00:20:18,839 --> 00:20:20,119
[SPEAKER_00] u tom smjeru.

329
00:20:22,319 --> 00:20:22,880
[SPEAKER_00] Nadalje,

330
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:24,220
[SPEAKER_00] Tomas je

331
00:20:24,220 --> 00:20:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] bio privržen

332
00:20:27,380 --> 00:20:29,279
[SPEAKER_00] jako uz djeda i baku,

333
00:20:29,279 --> 00:20:32,599
[SPEAKER_00] te tu je još nječkao se

334
00:20:32,599 --> 00:20:33,880
[SPEAKER_00] da li krenuti

335
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:34,799
[SPEAKER_00] putem

336
00:20:34,799 --> 00:20:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] duhovnosti

337
00:20:36,539 --> 00:20:37,160
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne.

338
00:20:39,880 --> 00:20:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] No smrt djeda i bake

339
00:20:41,599 --> 00:20:43,740
[SPEAKER_00] kojima je bio vrlo odan,

340
00:20:43,740 --> 00:20:45,759
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno občenito smrt

341
00:20:45,759 --> 00:20:46,759
[SPEAKER_00] voljenih osoba,

342
00:20:46,759 --> 00:20:48,359
[SPEAKER_00] ujerava čovjeka

343
00:20:48,359 --> 00:20:49,460
[SPEAKER_00] da je ovaj svijet

344
00:20:49,460 --> 00:20:50,200
[SPEAKER_00] prolazan.

345
00:20:50,200 --> 00:20:51,359
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi rekli,

346
00:20:51,359 --> 00:20:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] danas jeci,

347
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:52,700
[SPEAKER_00] sutra nisi

348
00:20:52,700 --> 00:20:55,400
[SPEAKER_00] i ono nas

349
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] otvara prema

350
00:20:56,380 --> 00:20:57,299
[SPEAKER_00] transcendentnom,

351
00:20:57,299 --> 00:20:58,640
[SPEAKER_00] prema božanskom.

352
00:20:58,640 --> 00:21:00,299
[SPEAKER_00] I upravo se to

353
00:21:00,299 --> 00:21:00,880
[SPEAKER_00] smrću

354
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:03,640
[SPEAKER_00] Tomasove bake i djeda

355
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] dogodilo.

356
00:21:05,299 --> 00:21:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] tu je on dobio poriv

357
00:21:06,420 --> 00:21:07,480
[SPEAKER_00] da

358
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:10,160
[SPEAKER_00] više komunicira

359
00:21:10,160 --> 00:21:10,680
[SPEAKER_00] s Bogom.

360
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] Stvorila se ta želja u njemu,

361
00:21:12,539 --> 00:21:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] pojavila se ta želja

362
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:14,700
[SPEAKER_00] na komunikaciju

363
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:15,019
[SPEAKER_00] s Bogom

364
00:21:15,019 --> 00:21:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] din na neku

365
00:21:15,619 --> 00:21:16,740
[SPEAKER_00] višu razinu.

366
