[SPEAKER_00] nisam baš control freak,

1063
00:38:02,340 --> 00:38:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali volim imati sve pod kontrolom,

1064
00:38:04,460 --> 00:38:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] volim znati

1065
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:07,699
[SPEAKER_00] i imati stvari na svojem mjestu.

1066
00:38:07,699 --> 00:38:09,280
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da sam tu vidio

1067
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:12,719
[SPEAKER_00] lagano gubim konce u svojim rukama.

1068
00:38:13,340 --> 00:38:14,280
[SPEAKER_00] No, ok,

1069
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] pustio sam da

1070
00:38:16,460 --> 00:38:19,179
[SPEAKER_00] to teče dalje.

1071
00:38:19,179 --> 00:38:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] Tada još nisam znao.

1072
00:38:20,159 --> 00:38:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pardon,

1073
00:38:22,460 --> 00:38:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] tada još nisam znao kakva je to faza.

1074
00:38:24,380 --> 00:38:26,360
[SPEAKER_00] I

1075
00:38:26,360 --> 00:38:29,260
[SPEAKER_00] da bi stvar bila još gora,

1076
00:38:29,260 --> 00:38:29,940
[SPEAKER_00] sad ne znam,

1077
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] prvu ili drugu noć.

1078
00:38:31,199 --> 00:38:33,860
[SPEAKER_00] Znači to je bio kraj trećeg mjeseca.

1079
00:38:33,860 --> 00:38:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] U ulici je počelo snježiti.

1080
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] I

1081
00:38:37,519 --> 00:38:38,460
[SPEAKER_00] u roku

1082
