[SPEAKER_00] par sati po noći

1083
00:38:40,420 --> 00:38:41,880
[SPEAKER_00] kada sam ja bio budan,

1084
00:38:41,880 --> 00:38:43,280
[SPEAKER_00] naravno gledajući taj snijeg,

1085
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] te pahodje koje su padale,

1086
00:38:44,380 --> 00:38:46,099
[SPEAKER_00] napalo je pola metra snijega.

1087
00:38:46,099 --> 00:38:47,300
[SPEAKER_00] Puh,

1088
00:38:47,300 --> 00:38:48,719
[SPEAKER_00] totalni kolaps.

1089
00:38:48,719 --> 00:38:51,820
[SPEAKER_00] Znači tad su još krenule misli.

1090
00:38:51,820 --> 00:38:53,320
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, sad će mi trebati 20 minuta

1091
00:38:53,320 --> 00:38:55,119
[SPEAKER_00] da očistim auto.

1092
00:38:55,119 --> 00:38:56,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ako su ceste prohodne,

1093
00:38:56,980 --> 00:38:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] treba će mi dva, dva i pol sata

1094
00:38:58,460 --> 00:38:59,260
[SPEAKER_00] jer pada snijeg.

1095
00:38:59,559 --> 00:39:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ako nisu prohodne,

1096
00:39:00,500 --> 00:39:02,159
