1098
00:39:03,639 --> 00:39:04,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ko zna, ako ću uopće moć?

1099
00:39:04,719 --> 00:39:06,679
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, sad ako je djete bolesno.

1100
00:39:06,679 --> 00:39:09,119
[SPEAKER_00] A tim trenucima se i

1101
00:39:09,119 --> 00:39:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] moj sin

1102
00:39:10,500 --> 00:39:11,760
[SPEAKER_00] budio

1103
00:39:11,760 --> 00:39:13,019
