1104
00:39:13,019 --> 00:39:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] jer je tražio hrane.

1105
00:39:14,500 --> 00:39:15,219
[SPEAKER_00] Bio je gladan.

1106
00:39:15,219 --> 00:39:16,900
[SPEAKER_00] I strano, šta mu je,

1107
00:39:16,900 --> 00:39:17,639
[SPEAKER_00] je li ovo dobro,

1108
