[SPEAKER_00] je li nije?

1109
00:39:18,059 --> 00:39:20,179
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, to je meni prvo djete.

1110
00:39:20,179 --> 00:39:22,360
[SPEAKER_00] Sad je to sve puno lakše.

1111
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:26,440
[SPEAKER_00] I tu su se nametnule te misli,

1112
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] ti osjećaj,

1113
00:39:27,639 --> 00:39:28,519
[SPEAKER_00] ti strahovi,

1114
00:39:29,119 --> 00:39:29,719
[SPEAKER_00] koje su,

1115
00:39:29,719 --> 00:39:31,179
[SPEAKER_00] evo, sad kako gledam,

1116
00:39:31,179 --> 00:39:32,659
[SPEAKER_00] sa odmakom vremena,

1117
00:39:32,659 --> 00:39:34,219
[SPEAKER_00] to je bila jedna

1118
00:39:34,219 --> 00:39:36,300
[SPEAKER_00] tamna noć duha,

1119
00:39:36,300 --> 00:39:36,739
[SPEAKER_00] duše,

1120
00:39:36,739 --> 00:39:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je Bog,

1121
00:39:37,380 --> 00:39:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je Bog te moje sjene,

1122
00:39:39,619 --> 00:39:41,860
[SPEAKER_00] tu moju organiziranost,

1123
