[SPEAKER_00] tu moju kontrolu,

1124
00:39:43,099 --> 00:39:44,940
[SPEAKER_00] uspio izvući,

1125
00:39:44,940 --> 00:39:46,139
[SPEAKER_00] ali svojom voljom.

1126
00:39:46,920 --> 00:39:48,280
[SPEAKER_00] i to je to pasivno čišćenje,

1127
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:49,400
[SPEAKER_00] ja tu nisam imao kontrole,

1128
