[SPEAKER_00] ja nisam jeo,

1129
00:39:50,159 --> 00:39:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] nisam spavo,

1130
00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] nisam mogo moliti.

1131
00:39:52,380 --> 00:39:53,300
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavno,

1132
